<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>ActivityKit on LYon's Blog</title><link>https://yindongliang.com/docs/Apple/Frameworks/ActivityKit/</link><description>Recent content in ActivityKit on LYon's Blog</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>zh-cn</language><atom:link href="https://yindongliang.com/docs/Apple/Frameworks/ActivityKit/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>添加交互式按钮</title><link>https://yindongliang.com/docs/Apple/Frameworks/ActivityKit/%E4%BA%A4%E4%BA%92%E5%BC%8F%E6%8C%89%E9%92%AE/</link><pubDate>Sat, 24 May 2025 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://yindongliang.com/docs/Apple/Frameworks/ActivityKit/%E4%BA%A4%E4%BA%92%E5%BC%8F%E6%8C%89%E9%92%AE/</guid><description>&lt;p>在 iOS 中使用 ActivityKit 实现锁屏计时器的暂停功能并添加按钮，可以通过以下步骤实现：&lt;/p>
&lt;hr>
&lt;h3 id="1-定义-activity-属性">1. ​&lt;strong>定义 Activity 属性&lt;/strong>​&lt;a class="anchor" href="#1-%e5%ae%9a%e4%b9%89-activity-%e5%b1%9e%e6%80%a7">#&lt;/a>&lt;/h3>
&lt;p>在 &lt;code>ActivityAttributes&lt;/code> 中添加 &lt;code>isPaused&lt;/code> 状态：&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#b0c4de;background-color:#282c34;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;">&lt;code class="language-swift" data-lang="swift">&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#76a9f9">struct&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#ca72ff">TimerAttributes&lt;/span>&lt;span style="color:#abb2bf">:&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#aa89ea">ActivityAttributes&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#abb2bf">{&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> &lt;span style="color:#76a9f9">public&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#76a9f9">struct&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#ca72ff">ContentState&lt;/span>&lt;span style="color:#abb2bf">:&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#aa89ea">Codable&lt;/span>&lt;span style="color:#abb2bf">,&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#e5c07b">Hashable&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#abb2bf">{&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> &lt;span style="color:#76a9f9">var&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#dcaeea">endTime&lt;/span>&lt;span style="color:#abb2bf">:&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#aa89ea">Date&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> &lt;span style="color:#76a9f9">var&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#dcaeea">isPaused&lt;/span>&lt;span style="color:#abb2bf">:&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#e5c07b">Bool&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#8a93a5;font-style:italic">// 暂停状态&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> &lt;span style="color:#abb2bf">}&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> &lt;span style="color:#8a93a5;font-style:italic">// 其他固定属性（如计时器总时长）&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#abb2bf">}&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;hr>
&lt;h3 id="2-创建处理暂停的-appintent">2. ​&lt;strong>创建处理暂停的 AppIntent&lt;/strong>​&lt;a class="anchor" href="#2-%e5%88%9b%e5%bb%ba%e5%a4%84%e7%90%86%e6%9a%82%e5%81%9c%e7%9a%84-appintent">#&lt;/a>&lt;/h3>
&lt;p>实现一个自定义的 &lt;code>AppIntent&lt;/code> 来响应按钮操作：&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>基础概念</title><link>https://yindongliang.com/docs/Apple/Frameworks/ActivityKit/%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80%E6%A6%82%E5%BF%B5/</link><pubDate>Mon, 19 May 2025 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://yindongliang.com/docs/Apple/Frameworks/ActivityKit/%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80%E6%A6%82%E5%BF%B5/</guid><description>&lt;p>Apple 的 &lt;strong>ActivityKit&lt;/strong> 是在 iOS 16 引入的一项框架，主要用于支持 &lt;strong>Live Activities（实时活动）&lt;/strong> 的功能。它允许 App 在锁屏和动态岛（iPhone 14 Pro 及以上）中显示动态更新的实时信息，比如计程车到达时间、外卖配送状态、比赛比分等。&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>计时器示例</title><link>https://yindongliang.com/docs/Apple/Frameworks/ActivityKit/%E8%AE%A1%E6%97%B6%E5%99%A8%E7%A4%BA%E4%BE%8B/</link><pubDate>Mon, 19 May 2025 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://yindongliang.com/docs/Apple/Frameworks/ActivityKit/%E8%AE%A1%E6%97%B6%E5%99%A8%E7%A4%BA%E4%BE%8B/</guid><description>&lt;p>下面我会帮你从零构建一个完整的 &lt;strong>计时器类 Live Activity 示例项目&lt;/strong>，分为两大部分：&lt;/p>
&lt;ol>
&lt;li>
&lt;p>&lt;strong>主 App（启动、更新、结束 Live Activity）&lt;/strong>&lt;/p>
&lt;/li>
&lt;li>
&lt;p>&lt;strong>Widget Extension（展示在锁屏 / 动态岛）&lt;/strong>&lt;/p></description></item></channel></rss>